text: I am proud that the state of Georgia is being represented by two remarkable athletes in the @USBSF bobsled team at the #2018Olympics. Please join me in wishing @Chrisak4298 from Stockbridge and @eamslider24 from Douglasville the very best of luck as they go for gold next week!
